title: DPS-BEST OF-for Aug 13, 2020
itunes:title: DPS-BEST OF-for Aug 13, 2020
description:
Dan Patrick shares the latest update on the Big Ten and Pac-12's decision to cancel the college football season and looks ahead to what the rest of the Power Five conferences will do. He speaks with UCLA head coach Chip Kelly about the cancellation of the season and NFL Network host Kyle Brandt opens up about his viral tweet that targeted members of the sports media.
